      "academic_group": "MB ChB Pgm Comm",
      "academic_org": "MB ChB Pgm Comm",
      "learning_outcomes": "After the SSM, the students should be able to:\n1. realize the importance of lifelong, self-directed learning, and\n2. appreciate the necessity of having skills to acquire new knowledge in order to meet the challenge of society's ever changing demands.",
      "course_syllabus": "Free choice of project areas will enable students to explore critically and pursue subjects and topics that excite them.",
